"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-11-China-s-high-tech-innovations-sparkle-at-2024-Paris-Olympics-1vYhZu1g3Ys-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  A car loaded with official Olympic Phryge mascots for 2024 Paris Olympics drives on the Champs-Elysees in Paris, France, July 19, 2024.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 307, \"end\": 321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"score\": 0.9992163039517089, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Champs-Elysees\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\"}, {\"begin\": 325, \"end\": 330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999449756, \"rank\": 5.5190100380665137e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 332, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999983689436936, \"rank\": 8.940798162577604e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CMG  With its bright eyes and warm smile, the Olympic Phryge mascot has gained in popularity as the Paris Olympics draws to a close.\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Data from the Paris Olympics Organizing Committee shows that 80 percent of the Phryges are manufactured in China.\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 504, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 597, \"end\": 602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999242054429, \"rank\": 6.541214218725084e-08, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Quanzhou Nanyang Arts & Crafts Co., Ltd. is a commissioned manufacturer of the event's mascots.\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Phryge is known for its unique standing posture, with its slender legs supporting a large body, making it a challenging design in the production process,\\\" said Jiang Lingyan, senior sales manager of the company.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The design team innovatively combined two types of polyvinyl chloride (PVC) material in one Phryge to address the potential bumps and impacts during international long-distance transport.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polyvinyl_chloride\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"polyvinyl chloride\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polyvinyl_chloride\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polyvinyl_chloride\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The legs are reinforced with rigid PVC, and the eyelashes are made from soft PVC to maintain the design's unique look, said Jiang.\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1233, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Jiang, 3D modeling and printing techniques were used during the sample design and production process to ensure precision in every detail.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1385, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also, to ensure each pair of eyes is vivid and expressive, the company controlled the distribution of ink and pressure.\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After numerous trials and improvements, the sample made six round trips between China and France over nine months before the Olympics opened.\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1587, \"end\": 1592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999242054429, \"rank\": 6.541214218725084e-08, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1597, \"end\": 1603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999983689436936, \"rank\": 8.940798162577604e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nanyang Arts & Crafts was commissioned to produce seven types of resin figurines and two types of keychains in various sizes and designs, totaling 200,000 pieces.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Comfortable sportswear provides athletes with the support they need to achieve great results.\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China's sportswear brand Peak cooperated with the Olympic committees of 11 countries to offer sportswear and suits for athletes.\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 2035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1907, \"end\": 1912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999242054429, \"rank\": 6.541214218725084e-08, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1926, \"end\": 1936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brand_Peak\", \"score\": 0.9999999958431545, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"brand Peak\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brand_Peak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brand_Peak\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"By working with these Olympic committees, we showcase China's high-quality products, along with our unique understanding and innovative capabilities in sports equipment,\\\" said Xu Jingnan, chairman of the board at PEAK.\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2256, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2092, \"end\": 2097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999242054429, \"rank\": 6.541214218725084e-08, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 2217, \"end\": 2224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jingnan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jingnan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jingnan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jingnan\"}, {\"begin\": 2251, \"end\": 2255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peak_Sport_Products\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.501013939473214e-18, \"text\": \"PEAK\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peak_Sport_Products\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peak_Sport_Products\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ANTA, another Chinese sportswear manufacturer, provides Chinese athletes with team uniforms for medal ceremonies.\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2272, \"end\": 2279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9039633467587596, \"rank\": 0.10622785683802165, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 2314, \"end\": 2321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9039633467587596, \"rank\": 0.10622785683802165, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are made from eco-friendly materials, such as recycled nylon and recycled polyester, achieving a carbon reduction of over 50 percent.\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To make customized shoes for athletes, we set up a laboratory that has three tracks to simulate different running environments.\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also, technologies including foot scanners and a 3D motion capture system are employed,\\\" said Zheng Zhiyi, chief scientist of ANTA Sports Science Lab.\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2735, \"end\": 2740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"score\": 0.9872135632139797, \"rank\": 0.01295203871875926, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\"}, {\"begin\": 2741, \"end\": 2746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhiyi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zhiyi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2566598\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhiyi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhiyi\"}, {\"begin\": 2767, \"end\": 2778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anta_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ANTA Sports\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anta_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anta_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beyond the stadiums, drones shift positions in the sky to form various shapes, including that of an Olympic torchbearer.\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2913, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Over 50 LED screens shipped from China are deployed around Paris to offer livestreaming services for spectators.\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 3026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2947, \"end\": 2952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999242054429, \"rank\": 6.541214218725084e-08, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 2973, \"end\": 2978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999449756, \"rank\": 5.5190100380665137e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These advanced technological products are all developed and manufactured in China.\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3103, \"end\": 3108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999242054429, \"rank\": 6.541214218725084e-08, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Zhao Kai, vice president of the LED screen provider Absen, the screens are notable for their high stability and energy efficiency.\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3124, \"end\": 3128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhao_Mengfu\", \"score\": 0.990892223617156, \"rank\": 0.009185080598149709, \"text\": \"Zhao\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhao_Mengfu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhao_Mengfu\"}, {\"begin\": 3129, \"end\": 3132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajoran\", \"score\": 0.8650149056078759, \"rank\": 0.15597706889551832, \"text\": \"Kai\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajoran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajoran\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is estimated that an outdoor LED screen covering an area of 2,000 square meters can cut energy consumption by 20 percent compared to traditional screens.\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3411, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We not only provide green LED display solutions but also showcase the company's technological innovation and commitment to exploring new advancements,\\\" said Zhao.\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3571, \"end\": 3575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhao_Mengfu\", \"score\": 0.990892223617156, \"rank\": 0.009185080598149709, \"text\": \"Zhao\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhao_Mengfu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhao_Mengfu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3838, \"entities\": []}]}"